verbose_text: Adam10, the disintegrin and metalloprotease that modulates the cell adhesion role of Pcdh gamma displayed the largest synergome (28.0%), while spastic paraplegia 7 homolog (Spg7), encoding a protein involved in anterograde axon cargo transport, had the largest antagome (28%).
